      "code": "self.self = /* ? */;\nif ((parent && SSF2API.isReady()) || self.self) {\n\tself.self.setGlobalVariable(\"nStoredLabel\", null);\n\tself.self.setGlobalVariable(\"sStoredLabel\", null);\n\tself.self.setLandingLag(false);\n}\nif ((parent && SSF2API.isReady()) || self.self) {\n\tself.playsound = SSF2API.random();\n\tself.audio = self.self.getGlobalVariable(\"audio\");\n}\nreturn;",
