      "code": "self.self.addEffectToList(self.self.attachEffect(\"trail_link_bair\", { scaleX: 1.1, scaleY: 1.1, parentLock: true, syncHitStun: true }));\nself.self.clearEffectsOnStateChange();\nreturn;",
