      "code": "self.self.removeAllEffects();\nSSF2API.getCamera().shake(5);\nif (self.self.getMetalStatus()) {\n\tself.self.playSound(\"metal_land_l\");\n\treturn;\n}\nself.self.playAttackSound(2);",
