      "code": "self.self.updateAttackBoxStats(1, { power: 45, damage: 12, direction: 37, kbConstant: 95 });\nself.self.refreshAttackID();\nself.self.addEffectToList(self.self.attachEffect(\"slash_link_fairf\", { scaleX: 1.1, scaleY: 1.1, parentLock: true, syncHitStun: true }));\nreturn;",
